## Guardrails
- Every trade action must have a log entry before and after — no silent actions
- Every skip decision must log the reason — "no signal" is a valid reason, silence is not
- Never log PII or sensitive data (API keys, private key material) — even in DEBUG
- Log files must be rotated — unbounded logs fill disk and kill the bot
- CRITICAL level must always trigger an alert — don't use it for anything non-critical
